{"tid":1741620,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《抗暴之戰》首先推動全民運動，全民健身，然後全民習武，最後達至\"全民勇武\"","createTime":"2019-11-20T12:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T08:46:43.000Z","uid":293677,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf407b677bd2dea567c7c55efae53f7096a1211","tid":1741620,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"古語有云：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">修身</span></span>齊家治國平天下<br />\n要做大事，就要先裝備好自己<br />\n我地依家係要打仗要革命<br />\n但係你地做好左備準未??<br />\n所謂做準備<br />\n唔只係講緊心態同足夠既gear<br />\n我知道有唔少上前線既手足已經有戰死的心理準備<br />\n而且寫好左遣書<br />\n想同班癲狗死過<br />\n但係現實D黎睇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地太弱</span></span><br />\n我地必須要認清呢個事實<br />\n無可否認<br />\n我地人數上完全佔優<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係點解我地大部分時間都係輸?<br />\n就係因為我地太弱</span></strong></span><br />\n我地唔係輸心態<br />\n亦唔係輸人數同gear<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地係輸身體質素</span></span><br />\n大家睇清楚班狂暴狗同畜龍<br />\n睇清楚佢地既身型體格<br />\n個個都受過嚴格體能訓練<br />\n你地要同佢隻揪?算把啦<br />\n如果純粹雙方都無gear之下對戰<br />\n即使我地人數係人地既三倍<br />\n一樣輸硬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更何況家陣人地除左身體質素比我地強<br />\n仲有埋基本格鬥術訓練同屈機既軍事裝備</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要贏<br />\n就要先收窄我地同對家既差距<br />\n從最基本做起：提升身體質素<br />\n<br />\n大方向就係：<br />\n全民運動，全民健身，<br />\n然後全民習武，<br />\n最後達至&quot;全民勇武&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你仲未開始，請你今日即刻開始<br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟從六月已經開始舉鐵，之後買埋奶粉飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自知體能太弱，上到戰場只係做炮灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係想提醒手足呢場係長期戰爭<br />\n唔好急於報仇，<br />\n我同各位一樣每日都好嬲好嬲好撚嬲<br />\n但係我知，我要忍辱負重<br />\n要將怒氣化為動力<br />\n我要令自己變強<br />\n最後引用普京一句說話：<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有實力的憤怒是毫無意義的</span></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n香港人，運動<br />\n香港人，健身<br />\n香港人，習武"},{"pid":"91891bf96091e4af826edccff192f57881551d08","tid":1741620,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人微言輕<br />\n我只係一個P牌仔<br />\n希望巴絲們幫推"},{"pid":"ec0e1ed141e21d7264462765b6501a612aa764bb","tid":1741620,"uid":87305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e911b3ab8ee3115157aa6c0e061e4fa875ea301","tid":1741620,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec0e1ed141e21d7264462765b6501a612aa764bb","tid":1741620,"uid":87305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油<br />\n一齊努力"},{"pid":"16b40bc6b0e51880a18b6019b5c53331edd7d39e","tid":1741620,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚只係跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7490259e5c8f9724302ebe5abb5c9a35f71c89","tid":1741620,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"點樣可以吸引多啲平時唔運動，活動嘅時候又企得後嘅人一齊健身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458d4dd22051041f0aef45762e33301eba874f06","tid":1741620,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b40bc6b0e51880a18b6019b5c53331edd7d39e","tid":1741620,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚只係跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas