k\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=428cee4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=5d424aa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=5e876fad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"65d77ba6513ca0a03b02cbf367ce991ada1ff7f0","tid":1741620,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n隻角色唔夠基礎白值，話知你will power有幾強<br />\n一落實戰都會下風<br />\n<br />\n利伸 日日練緊"},{"pid":"3f528b8f93d4b4dc6e3f1ec7b3a4e5f73fb8b60b","tid":1741620,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:37:08.000Z","msg":"各區有無人搞健身、防身、格鬥班？開唔開TG?"},{"pid":"c062cf1cb37cf5e9d822fbc0a7c7b87f48df5cd7","tid":1741620,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6bf5374d6ae158943a66d9097c0ee7428caea0","tid":1741620,"uid":46411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"點解要推全部人做勇武呢.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"加大隻角色嘅自由度有咩問題？<br />\n有勇武級嘅能力值果陣，勇武又得、做和理非又得，自由變換<br />\n<br />\n再者，都講左好耐啦<br />\n亂世之中，要自己保護自己，對住藍絲/出事果陣唔通報狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89945e03d10207a79f47807dc0d437179151237f","tid":1741620,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21